    {
      "start_time": 76.0,
      "end_time": 114.0,
      "transcript": "마침 에드컨웨이가 세계 지식 포럼을 위해서 한국에 들어와 있다고 해서 연락을 취하게 됐고요 오늘 에드컨웨이와 직접 대화를 나눠보겠습니다 감사합니다. remember actually from early when I was starting to understand economics called iPencil about telling the story of how a pencil is made from the perspective of the pencil and it's saying I'm a pencil I am one of the simplest things you can possibly imagine but there is no single person in the world who understands how to make me",
